## File Map

### After cleanup (~22 files)

```
src/openplan/
  __init__.py           # VERSION
  __main__.py           # CLI entry
  cli.py                # Auth, subscribe, status
  config.py             # Config loader
  server.py             # MCP protocol handler
  handler_utils.py      # RW locks, cursor, ok(), err()

  handlers/
    __init__.py          # HANDLERS dict
    plan_handler.py      # plan tool
    checkpoint_handler.py # checkpoint tool
    review_handler.py     # review tool
    manage_handler.py     # manage tool

  core/
    plan.py              # Goal decomposition, route generation
    checkpoint.py        # Phase completion, deviation, reroute, evidence
    review.py            # Retrospective, learnings, mesh status
    manage.py            # Graph mutations (revert, set_cursor, delete, archive)
    graph.py             # Health, search, scoring (activation inlined)
    costs.py             # Defaults, calibration
    learning.py          # tune(), bandit (bandit inlined)
    telemetry.py         # Checkpoint capture, Mesh sync, degraded mode
    planner.py           # A* pathfinding
    goals.py             # Goal parsing
    ids.py               # ID generation

  db/
    connection.py        # get_connection
    schema.py            # All CREATE TABLE statements
```

**Net change**: 52 files → ~22 files. 4 tools instead of 6. 1 prompt instead of 2.

